"><div class="media-object-video"><div class="wsj-media-summary clearfix"><div class="strap-container"><h4 class="strap" itemprop="description"></h4></div></div><iframe width="400" height="225" src="https://video-api.wsj.com/api-video/player/v3/iframe.html?guid=D92112D3-1820-448C-AE31-7108C18E7810&amp;height=225&amp;width=400&amp;plid=video_amp&amp;chainVideos=true&amp;parentUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2Fspecial-counsel-2024-election-trump-hunter-biden-david-weiss-merrick-garland-archer-burisma-smith-877d416&amp;a=a" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></iframe><p class="imageCaption">仙境：现在困扰唐纳德·特朗普和亨特·拜登的法律问题的核心是“没有人可以凌驾于法律之上”。瓦格纳集团的叶夫根尼·普里戈任提供了另一种选择：没有规则。图片：美联社/法新社/盖蒂图片社 综合：马克·凯利<span class="imageCredit">华尔街日报互动版</span></p></div></div></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 11 Aug 2023 22:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/special-counsel-2024-election-trump-hunter-biden-david-weiss-merrick-garland-archer-burisma-smith-877d416</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/special-counsel-2024-election-trump-hunter-biden-david-weiss-merrick-garland-archer-burisma-smith-877d416<category>一月6探头</category><category>机密文件调查</category><category>2024 年总统竞选</category><category>共和党初选</category><category>腐败</category><category>布里斯马</category><category>德文弓箭手</category><category>特别顾问</category><category>逃税</category><category>认罪协议</category><category>企业/行业新闻</category><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>犯罪/法律诉讼</category><category>政治/国际关系</category><category>国内政治</category><category>选举</category><category>国家/总统选举</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论/意见</category><category>法激活过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>梅里克·加兰</category><category>亨特·拜登</category><category>唐纳德·特朗普</category><category>公司的</category><category>行业新闻</category><category>政治的</category><category>一般新闻</category><category>犯罪</category><category>合